name: The Girl is Mine
blurb: Tom and Ross introduce, discuss and perhaps confuse the concept before navigating our first star studded voyage.

name: Don't Give Up
blurb: Only episode two and our format already causes us problems… But we will not give up!

name: Another Way to Die
blurb: We start a new round inspired by the question Ross asked last time.. Are there any Bond duets?? Bond geekery threatened to ensue, and was difficult to contain. Luckily we created a safe word.. ‘Spectre’.

name: Nothing Compares 2 U
blurb: Tom and Ross have been away. And they’ve missed each other. Eating dinner in fancy restaurants, seeing whomever they choose, yeah sure, great, but 2 is always better than 1. And U, well it’s better than just me. A man who knows this all too well is The Purple One. And he knows there’s much to be Gained from a team up, yup there’s a whole lotta Rosie right here too. Which is a good job because he is thoroughly bereft.
